thread.title: Cheers and a business challenge greet freed Saudi tycoons

title: Cheers and a business challenge greet freed Saudi tycoons
text:
Cheers and a business challenge greet freed Saudi tycoons 6:57am EST - 02:07 
Cheering supporters greeted Saudi Arabian billionaire Prince Alwaleed bin Talal when he arrived at his skyscraper offices in Riyadh after his release from detention in an anti-corruption crackdown. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
